---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us — Resurgence Builds"
  description="Get in touch with the Resurgence Builds team. Report issues, submit corrections, propose partnerships, or just say hello."
  keywords={["contact resurgence builds", "division resurgence contact", "resurgence builds feedback"]}
>
  <div class="container section content-width">
    <h1 class="heading-accent">Contact Us</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>Have a question, correction, or partnership inquiry? We read everything. Pick the best channel below and we'll get back to you.</p>

      <h2>General Inquiries &amp; Feedback</h2>
      <p>For general questions, build discussions, or just to say hello — our Discord is the fastest way to reach us. You'll find the <strong>#report-website-issues</strong> channel for site-related feedback and <strong>#general</strong> for everything else.</p>
      <div style="margin: var(--sp-4) 0;">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/t6GTR6tpd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--primary" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13.545 2.907a13.2 13.2 0 0 0-3.257-1.011.05.05 0 0 0-.052.025c-.141.25-.297.577-.406.833a12.2 12.2 0 0 0-3.658 0 8 8 0 0 0-.412-.833.05.05 0 0 0-.052-.025c-1.125.194-2.22.534-3.257 1.011a.04.04 0 0 0-.021.018C.356 6.024-.213 9.047.066 12.032q.003.022.021.037a13.3 13.3 0 0 0 3.995 2.02.05.05 0 0 0 .056-.019q.463-.63.818-1.329a.05.05 0 0 0-.01-.059l-.018-.011a9 9 0 0 1-1.248-.595.05.05 0 0 1-.02-.066l.015-.019q.127-.095.248-.195a.05.05 0 0 1 .051-.007c2.619 1.196 5.454 1.196 8.041 0a.05.05 0 0 1 .053.007q.121.1.248.195a.05.05 0 0 1-.004.085 8 8 0 0 1-1.249.594.05.05 0 0 0-.03.03.05.05 0 0 0 .003.041c.24.465.515.909.817 1.329a.05.05 0 0 0 .056.019 13.2 13.2 0 0 0 4.001-2.02.05.05 0 0 0 .021-.037c.334-3.451-.559-6.449-2.366-9.106a.03.03 0 0 0-.02-.019m-8.198 7.307c-.789 0-1.438-.724-1.438-1.612s.637-1.613 1.438-1.613c.807 0 1.45.73 1.438 1.613 0 .888-.637 1.612-1.438 1.612m5.316 0c-.788 0-1.438-.724-1.438-1.612s.637-1.613 1.438-1.613c.807 0 1.451.73 1.438 1.613 0 .888-.631 1.612-1.438 1.612"/></svg>
          Join Our Discord
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2>Corrections &amp; Fact Checks</h2>
      <p>Found a wrong stat, outdated talent description, or a build that no longer works after a patch? Drop it in <strong>#report-website-issues</strong> on Discord with the page URL and what's wrong. We fix verified corrections within 24 hours.</p>

      <h2>Press &amp; Partnership Inquiries</h2>
      <p>For press coverage, content creator collaborations, or business inquiries, reach out to us via email:</p>
      <p style="margin: var(--sp-2) 0;">
        <a href="mailto:contact@resurgencebuilds.com" style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm);">contact@resurgencebuilds.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Social Media</h2>
      <p>Follow us for build updates, patch analysis, and community highlights:</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--sp-3); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--sp-4);">
        <a href="https://x.com/ResurgenceBuild" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--outline" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M12.6.75h2.454l-5.36 6.142L16 15.25h-4.937l-3.867-5.07-4.425 5.07H.316l5.733-6.57L0 .75h5.063l3.495 4.633L12.601.75Zm-.86 13.028h1.36L4.323 2.145H2.865l8.875 11.633Z"/></svg>
          X / Twitter
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ResurgenceBuilds" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--outline" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8.051 1.999h.089c.822.003 4.987.033 6.11.335a2.01 2.01 0 0 1 1.415 1.42c.101.38.172.883.22 1.402l.01.104.022.26.008.104c.065.914.073 1.77.074 1.957v.075c-.001.194-.01 1.108-.082 2.06l-.008.105-.009.104c-.05.572-.124 1.14-.235 1.558a2.01 2.01 0 0 1-1.415 1.42c-1.16.312-5.569.334-6.18.335h-.142c-.309 0-1.587-.006-2.927-.052l-.17-.006-.087-.004-.171-.007-.171-.007c-1.11-.049-2.167-.128-2.654-.26a2.01 2.01 0 0 1-1.415-1.419c-.111-.417-.185-.986-.235-1.558L.09 9.82l-.008-.104A31 31 0 0 1 0 7.68v-.123c.002-.215.01-.958.064-1.778l.007-.103.003-.052.008-.104.022-.26.01-.104c.048-.519.119-1.023.22-1.402a2.01 2.01 0 0 1 1.415-1.42c.487-.13 1.544-.21 2.654-.26l.17-.007.172-.006.086-.003.171-.007A100 100 0 0 1 7.858 2zM6.4 5.209v4.818l4.157-2.408z"/></svg>
          YouTube
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/ResurgenceBuilds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--outline" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M6.167 8a.83.83 0 0 0-.83.83c0 .459.372.84.83.831a.831.831 0 0 0 0-1.661m1.843 3.647c.315 0 1.403-.038 1.976-.611a.23.23 0 0 0 0-.306.213.213 0 0 0-.306 0c-.353.363-1.126.487-1.67.487-.545 0-1.308-.124-1.671-.487a.213.213 0 0 0-.306 0 .213.213 0 0 0 0 .306c.564.563 1.652.61 1.977.61zm.992-2.807c0 .458.373.83.831.83s.83-.381.83-.83a.831.831 0 0 0-1.66 0zM16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.828-1.165c-.397 0-.763.16-1.029.426C9.948 6.457 8.556 5.98 7.067 5.934l.586-2.77 1.917.42a.84.84 0 0 0 1.67-.098.84.84 0 0 0-.83-.839.84.84 0 0 0-.744.468l-2.141-.459a.2.2 0 0 0-.233.153L6.69 5.925c-1.527.027-2.956.504-4.164 1.317a1.469 1.469 0 0 0-2.5 1.038c-.007.26.062.517.199.739a1.48 1.48 0 0 0-.058.39c0 1.994 2.327 3.612 5.192 3.612s5.192-1.618 5.192-3.611c0-.136-.02-.27-.058-.391.273-.416.312-.946.109-1.399a1.47 1.47 0 0 0-.774-.776z"/></svg>
          Reddit
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2>DMCA &amp; Copyright</h2>
      <p>For DMCA takedown requests and copyright concerns, please review our <a href="/dmca/">DMCA Policy</a> for the full process and required information.</p>

      <h2>Response Times</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Discord:</strong> Usually within a few hours (we're in there daily)</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> 1–3 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Corrections:</strong> Verified fixes deployed within 24 hours</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
